{"id":826,"parent_id":822,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":826,"title":"Lamentations 4","subtitle":"","short_title":"Lam.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 4"],[".studySummary",["i","The condition of Zion is pitiful because of sin and iniquity."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.1","order":"02.26.004.54858"},["b","1"],"How is the gold become dim!",["i","how"],"is the most fine gold changed! the stones of the sanctuary are poured out in the top of every street."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.2","order":"02.26.004.54859"},["b","2"],"The precious sons of Zion, comparable to fine gold, how are they esteemed as earthen pitchers, the work of the hands of the potter!"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.3","order":"02.26.004.54860"},["b","3"],"Even the sea monsters draw out the breast, they give suck to their young ones: the daughter of my people",["i","is become"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"cruel"],", like the ostriches in the wilderness."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.4","order":"02.26.004.54861"},["b","4"],"The tongue of the sucking child cleaveth to the roof of his mouth for thirst: the young children ask",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"bread"],",",["i","and"],"no man breaketh",["i","it"],"unto them."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.5","order":"02.26.004.54862"},["b","5"],"They that did feed delicately are desolate in the streets: they that were brought up in scarlet embrace dunghills."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.6","order":"02.26.004.54863"},["b","6"],"For the punishment of the iniquity of the daughter of my people is greater than the punishment of the sin of Sodom, that was overthrown as in a moment, and no hands stayed on her."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.7","order":"02.26.004.54864"},["b","7"],"Her Nazarites were purer than snow, they were whiter than milk, they were more ruddy in body than rubies, their polishing",["i","was"],"of sapphire:"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.8","order":"02.26.004.54865"},["b","8"],"Their visage is blacker than a coal; they are not known in the streets: their skin cleaveth to their bones; it is withered, it is become like a stick."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.9","order":"02.26.004.54866"},["b","9"],["i","They that be"],"slain with the sword are better than",["i","they that be"],"slain with hunger: for these pine away, stricken through for",["i","want of"],"the fruits of the field."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.10","order":"02.26.004.54867"},["b","10"],"The hands of the pitiful",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"women"],"have",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"sodden"],"their own children: they were their",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"meat"],"in the destruction of the daughter of my people."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.11","order":"02.26.004.54868"},["b","11"],"The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath accomplished his fury; he hath poured out his fierce anger, and hath kindled a fire in Zion, and it hath devoured the foundations thereof."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.12","order":"02.26.004.54869"},["b","12"],"The kings of the earth, and all the inhabitants of the world, would not have believed that the adversary and the enemy should have entered into the gates of Jerusalem."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.13","order":"02.26.004.54870"},["b","13"],"¶For the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"sins"],"of her prophets,",["i","and"],"the iniquities of her priests, that have shed the blood of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"just"],"in the midst of her,"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.14","order":"02.26.004.54871"},["b","14"],"They have wandered",["i","as"],"blind",["i","men"],"in the streets, they have polluted themselves with blood, so that men could not touch their garments."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.15","order":"02.26.004.54872"},["b","15"],"They cried unto them, Depart ye;",["i","it is"],"unclean; depart, depart, touch not: when they fled away and wandered, they said among the heathen, They shall no more sojourn",["i","there."]],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.16","order":"02.26.004.54873"},["b","16"],"The anger of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath divided them; he will no more regard them: they respected not the persons of the priests, they favoured not the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"elders"],"."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.17","order":"02.26.004.54874"},["b","17"],"As for us, our eyes as yet failed for our vain help: in our watching we have watched for a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"nation"],["i","that"],"could not save",["i","us."]],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.18","order":"02.26.004.54875"},["b","18"],"They hunt our steps, that we cannot go in our streets: our end is near, our days are fulfilled; for our",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"end"],"is come."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.19","order":"02.26.004.54876"},["b","19"],"Our persecutors are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"swifter"],"than the eagles of the heaven: they pursued us upon the mountains, they laid wait for us in the wilderness."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.20","order":"02.26.004.54877"},["b","20"],"The breath of our nostrils, the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"anointed"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", was taken in their",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"pits"],", of whom we said, Under his shadow we shall live among the heathen."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.21","order":"02.26.004.54878"},["b","21"],"¶Rejoice and be glad, O daughter of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"Edom"],", that dwellest in the land of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"Uz"],"; the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_21c"},"cup"],"also shall pass through unto thee: thou shalt be drunken, and shalt make thyself naked."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.22","order":"02.26.004.54879"},["b","22"],"¶The punishment of thine iniquity is accomplished, O daughter of Zion; he will no more carry thee away into captivity: he will visit thine iniquity, O daughter of Edom; he will discover thy sins."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.3a","order":"02.26.004.54880"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/job/39.16.13-16"},"Job 39:16 (13–16)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/cruelty"},"TG Cruelty"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.4a","order":"02.26.004.54882"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/52.6"},"Jer. 52:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.10a","order":"02.26.004.54884"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/woman"},"TG Woman"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.10b","order":"02.26.004.54886"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/26.29"},"Lev. 26:29"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/28.57.56-57"},"Deut. 28:57 (56–57)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.10c","order":"02.26.004.54888"},["b","10c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.9"},"Jer. 19:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.13a","order":"02.26.004.54890"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/5.31"},"Jer. 5:31"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/13.27"},"Hel. 13:27"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.13b","order":"02.26.004.54892"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17.10"},"Mosiah 17:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/14.11"},"Alma 14:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/60.13"},"60:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.16a","order":"02.26.004.54894"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/28.50.49-51"},"Deut. 28:50 (49–51)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.23.23-24"},"2 Kgs. 2:23 (23–24)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/3.5"},"Isa. 3:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/2.12"},"1 Ne. 2:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.17a","order":"02.26.004.54896"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/30.7.5,7"},"Isa. 30:7 (5, 7)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/37.7"},"Jer. 37:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.18a","order":"02.26.004.54898"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.2.2-3,6"},"Ezek. 7:2 (2–3, 6)"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.19a","order":"02.26.004.54900"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.13"},"Jer. 4:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/39.5"},"39:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.20a","order":"02.26.004.54902"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/35.25"},"2 Chr. 35:25"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/39.7"},"Jer. 39:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.20b","order":"02.26.004.54904"},["b","20b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/19.8.4,8"},"Ezek. 19:8 (4, 8)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/122.7.5,7"},"D&C 122:7 (5, 7)"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.21a","order":"02.26.004.54906"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.7"},"Jer. 49:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/21.14"},"2 Ne. 21:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.21b","order":"02.26.004.54908"},["b","21b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/job/1.1"},"Job 1:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"21c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.21c","order":"02.26.004.54910"},["b","21c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.15.15-16"},"Jer. 25:15 (15–16)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/3.26"},"Mosiah 3:26"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/43.26.24-26"},"D&C 43:26 (24–26)"],"."]]}
